35
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:15,200
A call? From who?

36
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,000
My girlfriend.

37
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,400
You're so loyal. What about you?

38
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,700
I...

39
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,600
- I don't feel like going.
- Nice.

40
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:30,000
He's something else. He's too lazy to find an excuse.

41
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,600
You have a strong personality.

42
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,600
Fine. I'll go there myself.

43
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,100
My brother, what was your name again?

44
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:43,300
- Zheng...
- Zheng Sunian.

45
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:45,500
Zheng Sunian?

46
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:49,400
I remember now.

47
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,500
You're the person who got first place for the cultural course!

48
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:53,100
I'm not sure about that.

49
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,400
It is you!

50
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,400
You scored over 500 marks!

51
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,600
I didn't expect us to stay in the same room!

52
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,500
Aren't I lucky?

53
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:04,000
Little Niannian, let me treat you to a meal!

54
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,600
You can speak without touching me.

55
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,400
Don't be shy.

56
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,800
In the future, we'll be good buddies who will share the same pants.

57
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,600
Hurry, give me a hug!

58
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:15,400
Let me get some of that top student's aura.

59
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,800
<i>[Liuli Hutong]</i>

60
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:39,100
<i>[For the silliest person in the world, Zhang Qi. You mustn't lose your dorm keys]</i>

61
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,000
My little lord! Hurry up!

62
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,400
Your car is here! Hurry up!

63
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,800
I'm done.

64
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,400
Hurry!

65
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,500
Hey, you must be careful

66
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,400
since you're bringing so many things to the airport.

67
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,600
Be very careful. Don't lose them.

68
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:17,700
Don't worry. I'm an adult now.

69
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:21,900
You're still a child to me.

70
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,800
Put it in properly.

71
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,000
Done.

72
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,900
Give me the bag.

73
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:35,200
Study hard, okay?

74
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,500
And...

75
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,100
take good care of yourself.

76
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,700
Give me a hug.

77
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:51,000
Mom, don't worry.

78
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,400
I won't let you and Dad down.

79
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,000
Take care.

80
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:59,200
Little brat! Go now.

81
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,000
I'll make a move now.

82
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,500
My son,

83
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,800
I have something for you.

84
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,800
What? I don't lack money.

85
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,300
See you.

86
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,900
Go now.

87
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,700
What a little brat.

88
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:31,300
Hubby, congratulations.

89
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:35,400
Our son has made us proud.

90
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:39,000
He got himself a slot in UTSC.

91
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,100
He has made us proud.

92
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:51,700
Thank you for gifting me with such a great son.

93
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:59,100
Actually, I've been blaming you all these years.

94
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,300
But now,

95
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,400
all those years of hardships that I'd endured,

96
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,500
I think they were worth it.

97
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,800
Can you see it?

98
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,800
I always wear it on my finger.

99
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:31,000
I will never remove it.

100
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:36,000
I want you to return the favor you owed me

101
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,200
in your next life.

102
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:42,800
You need to treat us extra well in our next lifetime.

103
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:45,700
You aren't allowed to abandon us and leave before us next time.

104
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,200
Got it?

105
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:55,300
<i>[Always Remembered]</i>

106
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,300
Ms. Yu. Ms. Yu!

107
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:12,500
Someone is waiting for you at the entrance.

108
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,600
Xin Jie?

109
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,000
Why are you here?

110
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,400
I'm sure you didn't expect to see me here.

111
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,500
How's your health?

112
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,000
I used to lie down all the time.

113
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,100
It made my health worse.

114
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:41,200
Now, I'm trying to be active.

115
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,400
What is this?

116
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:49,000
Can you do me a favor and sell this for me?

117
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,900
Don't worry.

118
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:53,400
I didn't steal this.

119
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,600
I drew it myself.

120
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:12,200
Your drawing is exceptional.

121
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,000
I drew it many years ago.

122
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:17,000
I couldn't bear to part with it before.

123
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,300
Why are you selling this away?

124
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,500
You should keep it for yourself.

125
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:25,300
Some time ago, I fell sick again.

126
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:28,300
Now, my house is barely surviving.

127
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:32,300
Wu Huan is in a terrible state because of me.

128
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:36,000
I really have no choice.

129
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,300
You're the only person I can ask this favor.

130
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:46,100
Xin Jie, I can only give it a try.

131
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,600
You know this as well.

132
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,200
I don't know anyone

133
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,400
who knows how to appreciate such drawings.

134
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,000
Why don't I bring you to see Mr. Luo?

135
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,700
Let's go.

136
00:09:57,700 --> 00:10:00,500
It's fine as long as I can buy a meal with the money.

137
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:12,300
I'm too ashamed to see Master.

138
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,800
I'll be counting on you, then.

139
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,100
Please resume your work.

140
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,800
I'll return first.

141
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:26,600
Xin Jie, wait for me.

142
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,800
I'll get some money for you.

143
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,400
Are you mocking me?

144
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,000
I'm not your kin.

145
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,600
You don't owe me any money or favor.

146
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:38,800
I'm grateful enough that you're doing this favor for me.

147
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,700
See you then.

148
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:53,400
Dongge, thank you.

149
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:06,320
Guys, you guys are in your senior year now.

150
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:10,310
<i>[Towards NCEE and a better dream]</i>
You guys must think about the universities you would like to get into

151
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:11,919
and the courses you want to select.

152
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:14,210
<i>[Do your best and get into university]</i>
You must have a goal.

153
00:11:14,210 --> 00:11:16,219
Look at Zhang Qi. He had a goal in mind.

154
00:11:16,219 --> 00:11:18,219
Now, he has himself a slot at UTSC.

155
00:11:18,219 --> 00:11:21,739
That's why you guys need to make your decision beforehand.

156
00:11:21,739 --> 00:11:23,550
Class dismissed.

157
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:38,600
Xue, which course do you plan to pick?

158
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,650
I haven't made up my mind yet.

159
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:43,570
I'm so envious of you. You have such a clear goal.

160
00:11:43,570 --> 00:11:45,649
Okay, then. I'll attend my professional course now.

161
00:11:45,649 --> 00:11:48,010
- Goodbye.
- Bye!

162
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:53,900
Tang Ya, have you made up your mind? Which course did you pick?

163
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:55,170
I haven't made up my mind yet.

164
00:11:55,170 --> 00:11:58,630
I'm pretty bad at everything.

165
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:00,169
I'm in a dilemma as well.

166
00:12:00,169 --> 00:12:02,260
Initially, I thought of asking my parents about it.

167
00:12:02,260 --> 00:12:04,700
But I think they have no idea as well.

168
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:07,570
Tomorrow is the weekend, right? I think I'll go and ask Sunian about it.

169
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:08,740
I'm so envious of you.

170
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:11,639
You have so many friends that can assist you in making life decisions.

171
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:14,170
Wu Huan, what about you? Which course did you pick?

172
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:17,910
I don't plan on getting into any university.

173
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:19,359
I'm already attending interviews.

174
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,140
- Interviews?
- Interviews?

175
00:12:21,140 --> 00:12:23,569
I'm not cut out for studying. I plan to work.

176
00:12:23,569 --> 00:12:25,619
- What kind of work?
- Logistics.

177
00:12:25,619 --> 00:12:26,619
What's that?

178
00:12:26,619 --> 00:12:28,220
Online shopping is the current trend, right?

179
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,749
Logistics involves sending and packing the goods.

180
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,959
I think it has a lot of potential.

181
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:35,450
You're right. Now, more and more people are buying into the idea of online shopping. You have great foresight.

182
00:12:35,450 --> 00:12:36,629
I don't dare to brag about anything else,

183
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:39,050
but you guys will get free delivery when you buy things online in the future.

184
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:41,690
I'll remember that. I'll make a move first.

185
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:42,840
You guys can enjoy your chat. Goodbye.

186
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,280
Goodbye.

187
00:12:48,770 --> 00:12:50,019
Wu Huan,

188
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:53,260
are... are you free tomorrow?

189
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:54,500
What's the matter?

190
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:56,900
I...

191
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:58,860
I wish to treat you to a meal.

192
00:12:58,860 --> 00:13:01,579
I want to thank you for finding me a job at the supermarket.

193
00:13:01,579 --> 00:13:03,620
I should be the one thanking you instead.

194
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:07,140
The supervisor told me that you begged him to give me your wage

195
00:13:07,140 --> 00:13:09,720
and told him to lie to me that I got a raise.

196
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:12,629
How could he do this?

197
00:13:12,629 --> 00:13:14,340
He promised me that he'd keep it a secret.

198
00:13:14,340 --> 00:13:15,820
He shouldn't keep that a secret.

199
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:17,670
You must never do this again in the future.

200
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:20,600
Thank you. I'll make a move first.

201
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:24,810
Wu Huan!

202
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:33,020
Thank you for treating me as a friend.

203
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:35,870
See you.

204
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:05,320
Take a guess at whose gift this is.

205
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:11,549
You have no idea, right?

206
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:13,050
Listen up.

207
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:15,610
This is...

208
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:19,320
for you.

209
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:24,479
- Who gave it to me?
- Xue Ning, the beauty of the design course.

210
00:14:24,479 --> 00:14:27,930
My goodness. She's fair, rich, and beautiful.

211
00:14:27,930 --> 00:14:31,129
If you still care about that little girlfriend of yours,

212
00:14:31,129 --> 00:14:34,320
I'm willing to sacrifice myself for your sake.

213
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:37,260
You may go ahead.

214
00:14:39,530 --> 00:14:43,510
As the saying goes, "You should not covet

215
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:46,070
your friend's wife." Here, take it.

216
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:51,720
Hey, don't you think it's strange?

217
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:54,680
Why isn't anyone trying to court Little Niannian?

218
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:58,850
Look at his amazing figure and marvelous looks.

219
00:14:58,850 --> 00:15:01,240
Even a guy like me would fall for you.

220
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,290
Thank you for nothing, I guess.

221
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:08,370
Let's get straight into business. What kind of girl do you like?

222
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:10,380
I can introduce someone to you.

223
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:13,770
I have no interest in relationships.

224
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:16,380
So you've never been in a relationship before, am I right?

225
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:18,810
I can tell at first glance. You have no experience at all!

226
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:20,339
If so, you've found the right person.

227
00:15:20,339 --> 00:15:22,380
I'm truly an expert when it comes to relationships.

228
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:26,340
Listen, in the past, I was chased by an endless number of girls.

229
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:28,960
They were lining up in order to court me.

230
00:15:30,810 --> 00:15:33,870
What do you mean by that? You don't believe me?

231
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,139
I never boast.

232
00:15:35,139 --> 00:15:38,480
I can swear to the heavens.

233
00:15:54,645 --> 00:15:58,554
♪ My passion is just like a torch ♪

234
00:15:58,554 --> 00:16:02,255
♪ Lighting up the entire desert ♪

235
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:06,675
Take off your uniform first. If not, they won't dry off in time.

236
00:16:07,990 --> 00:16:13,124
♪ My passion is just like a torch ♪

237
00:16:14,435 --> 00:16:18,975
Come on. Come on.

238
00:16:33,830 --> 00:16:35,749
Sunian.

239
00:16:45,195 --> 00:16:46,884
Shouldn't you introduce her to us?

240
00:16:46,884 --> 00:16:49,625
So who is she?

241
00:16:49,625 --> 00:16:51,435
She's my neighbor.

242
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:54,250
<i>[To Sunian, the best person in the world, from Shao Xue]</i>

243
00:16:56,075 --> 00:17:00,345
Little Niannian, I think I know your weakness now.

244
00:17:03,195 --> 00:17:05,465
Little Niannian?

245
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,705
Let's go.

246
00:17:08,705 --> 00:17:09,954
We're leaving already?

247
00:17:09,954 --> 00:17:13,375
What? Do you still wish to see him naked?

248
00:17:15,275 --> 00:17:18,225
No thanks. Let's go.

249
00:17:18,805 --> 00:17:21,325
Visit us when you're free, okay?

250
00:17:21,325 --> 00:17:23,945
Remember to visit us.

251
00:17:28,845 --> 00:17:32,405
Do you believe that he's only treating her as his neighbor?

252
00:17:32,405 --> 00:17:34,705
That's none of your business.

253
00:17:35,435 --> 00:17:39,534
Sunian, your dorm mate looks pretty flippant.

254
00:17:39,534 --> 00:17:40,995
