513
00:34:20,635 --> 00:34:22,164
Don't move! Don't run!

514
00:34:22,164 --> 00:34:23,845
Mimi, come back!

515
00:34:23,845 --> 00:34:25,445
Why is it here?

516
00:34:25,445 --> 00:34:27,185
On your first day of college,

517
00:34:27,185 --> 00:34:31,545
it came into our house right after you left.

518
00:34:31,545 --> 00:34:33,635
After that, it didn't leave.

519
00:34:33,635 --> 00:34:35,804
Maybe it's because it's getting old

520
00:34:35,804 --> 00:34:37,855
and it doesn't feel like wandering anymore.

521
00:34:38,955 --> 00:34:41,755
Why did you come back suddenly today?

522
00:34:41,755 --> 00:34:43,824
I showed my friends around the Restoration Department today.

523
00:34:43,824 --> 00:34:45,785
I came back on the way.

524
00:34:45,785 --> 00:34:48,054
- Have you eaten then?
- Not yet.

525
00:34:48,054 --> 00:34:51,284
Great. I haven't eaten either. I'll make dinner.

526
00:34:53,285 --> 00:34:54,915
Noodles with black bean sauce.

527
00:35:15,405 --> 00:35:18,115
Dad, why didn't you tear off the calendar?

528
00:35:18,115 --> 00:35:20,075
It's September now.

529
00:35:23,595 --> 00:35:25,995
- Leaf through what?
- The calendar.

530
00:35:28,095 --> 00:35:29,905
I forgot about it.

531
00:35:40,105 --> 00:35:42,095
You forgot about it for an entire month?

532
00:36:01,735 --> 00:36:03,265
What's the matter?

533
00:36:05,085 --> 00:36:06,655
Nothing.

534
00:36:13,985 --> 00:36:16,445
I...

535
00:36:16,445 --> 00:36:18,745
I know. I burned the sauce.

536
00:36:19,905 --> 00:36:23,185
This... It's been too long since I last cooked.

537
00:36:23,185 --> 00:36:25,264
I forgot how to cook.

538
00:36:25,264 --> 00:36:27,805
Sunian, don't eat this. I'll make a new bowl of noodles for you.

539
00:36:27,805 --> 00:36:29,225
No need for that, Dad.

540
00:36:29,225 --> 00:36:32,204
I'll eat this. It's pretty good.

541
00:36:34,205 --> 00:36:37,135
I don't know what's wrong with me.

542
00:36:53,615 --> 00:36:55,415
Dad.

543
00:37:37,205 --> 00:37:39,524
Shiyin, explain this question to me.

544
00:37:39,524 --> 00:37:41,615
I don't know how to solve it.

545
00:37:41,615 --> 00:37:43,305
This one.

546
00:37:50,085 --> 00:37:52,455
Wu Huan, why are you only here now?

547
00:37:52,455 --> 00:37:53,834
I went for the job interview.

548
00:37:53,834 --> 00:37:56,135
How was it?

549
00:37:56,135 --> 00:37:58,195
I don't think it's going to end well.

550
00:37:58,195 --> 00:38:00,614
Don't give up. I'm sure you'll succeed next time.

551
00:38:00,614 --> 00:38:02,435
You can do it!

552
00:38:03,685 --> 00:38:05,575
How do I solve this?

553
00:38:19,295 --> 00:38:24,225
Wu Huan, I've searched for logistics companies near your house.

554
00:38:24,225 --> 00:38:27,554
Although they're small, it'll be convenient for you to take care of your mom.

555
00:38:27,554 --> 00:38:30,204
- Thanks.
- Don't mention it.

556
00:38:30,204 --> 00:38:33,434
I realized that there are many logistics companies around here after I searched for them.

557
00:38:33,434 --> 00:38:37,795
I'm sure you'll find a job.

558
00:38:37,795 --> 00:38:40,285
Xue, accompany me to refill my bottle.

559
00:38:40,285 --> 00:38:42,645
Didn't you just drink some water?

560
00:38:43,645 --> 00:38:46,515
Shiyin! Shiyin!

561
00:38:46,515 --> 00:38:48,275
Lin Shiyin!

562
00:38:48,275 --> 00:38:50,365
Why are you furious?

563
00:38:50,365 --> 00:38:51,985
I hate Tang Ya.

564
00:38:51,985 --> 00:38:53,234
Why?

565
00:38:53,234 --> 00:38:54,485
She always steals my things.

566
00:38:54,485 --> 00:38:57,114
First, she stole you from me. Now, she's stealing...

567
00:38:57,114 --> 00:39:00,145
I don't understand what you mean.

568
00:39:00,145 --> 00:39:02,695
Anyway, she always goes against me.

569
00:39:02,695 --> 00:39:06,164
But to me, it seems like you're going against her.

570
00:39:06,164 --> 00:39:08,834
How is that possible? Who are you siding with?

571
00:39:08,834 --> 00:39:12,454
Anyway, we're here to refill your bottle. Where's your bottle?

572
00:39:14,155 --> 00:39:17,505
Give me some of it after you've refilled yours.

573
00:39:17,505 --> 00:39:20,414
I guess art students like you are hard to read.

574
00:39:20,414 --> 00:39:22,424
Sunian is an art student as well.

575
00:39:22,424 --> 00:39:23,874
He's different from you.

576
00:39:23,874 --> 00:39:27,084
Eeny, meeny, miny, moe.

577
00:39:27,084 --> 00:39:29,164
Which one shall I pick?

578
00:39:29,164 --> 00:39:30,715
It is you then.

579
00:39:34,375 --> 00:39:36,245
You're finally back.

580
00:39:36,245 --> 00:39:37,634
Hurry!

581
00:39:37,634 --> 00:39:40,534
You don't know how excruciating it was for me for the past few days.

582
00:39:40,534 --> 00:39:42,155
Hurry and have a seat.

583
00:39:43,235 --> 00:39:45,315
I was just gone for one day, you know?

584
00:39:45,315 --> 00:39:47,115
It felt like a year to me.

585
00:39:47,115 --> 00:39:50,754
Even when Little Baibai came back, he didn't speak to me at all.

586
00:39:50,754 --> 00:39:53,424
No matter how hard I tried to cheer him up, he'd only utter words like:

587
00:39:53,424 --> 00:39:57,435
"Hmm, ah, oh."

588
00:39:58,645 --> 00:40:00,685
Where is he?

589
00:40:00,685 --> 00:40:03,374
He went to class. He's not back yet.

590
00:40:06,875 --> 00:40:09,365
We should let him cool down for some time.

591
00:40:09,365 --> 00:40:11,145
It will be good for him.

592
00:40:11,145 --> 00:40:15,005
To me, I can only feel his coldness.

593
00:40:15,635 --> 00:40:19,535
By the way, you know Xue Ning. Right?

594
00:40:19,535 --> 00:40:20,855
I don't.

595
00:40:20,855 --> 00:40:22,974
You don't even know the beauty of the design course?

596
00:40:22,974 --> 00:40:25,605
It's the girl who's been trying to court Little Baibai ever since the military training started.

597
00:40:25,605 --> 00:40:29,385
Listen up. I've witnessed something new today.

598
00:40:29,385 --> 00:40:33,064
Little Baibai was putting on a stern face so that no one would approach him.

599
00:40:33,064 --> 00:40:35,144
But that girl is something else. She wasn't afraid at all.

600
00:40:35,144 --> 00:40:36,645
Instead, she tried to cling on to him.

601
00:40:36,645 --> 00:40:40,294
She followed him from here all the way to the self-study room.

602
00:40:41,065 --> 00:40:43,235
Many girls were following you as well.

603
00:40:44,675 --> 00:40:46,675
You're right about that.

604
00:40:46,675 --> 00:40:49,875
But they aren't as beautiful as her.

605
00:40:51,795 --> 00:40:53,875
I'm perplexed.

606
00:40:53,875 --> 00:40:56,504
You and Little Baibai are on an equal footing.

607
00:40:56,504 --> 00:40:59,635
When school was in session, many girls were trying to know you.

608
00:40:59,635 --> 00:41:01,905
Now, all of them are gone.

609
00:41:05,645 --> 00:41:08,405
Maybe it's because of

610
00:41:08,405 --> 00:41:10,544
what I said in class.

611
00:41:10,544 --> 00:41:12,385
What did you say?

